<NEW>

There was a nod from LEO PRME as he accepted not only the readiness
from HYDRAs and his men, but also from the Maximals around him as
well.

Meanwhile CRYOTEK looked over his supplies that he had brought, making
sure they were safely stowed away. Maximals and Predacons no longer
had the large volumes of subspace 'room' that that used to be enjoyed
by the Autobots and Decepticons before the great reduction. However he
was still ready. He was basically carrying extra rations of energon as
well as basic repair supplies and tools he might need to cut and
splice with. It was not much, but it would do in a pinch.

"I have the co-ordinates." SANTON said as he held up the device. At a
nod from LEO he began to read them, "320.25 by 7218.60 Vector 187."
His words were cool and calm as he read them off.

"Everyone have them?" LEO said as he looked around. "You fliers are
going to have to stay in the air, while we ground pounders are going
to be here inside the jungle. We will be heading for the same
location."

LEO PRIME straightened, "Maximals, MAXIMIZE!" he said as he shifed
into his beast mode, that of a yellow and brown lion, his roar echoing
across the jungle, and at the same time the Fuzors, SANTON and WING
CALIBER changed form as well.

"Noctorro, Airhammer, Wing Caliber try to keep an optic on us from the
air, but if you loose sight of us, get to that location and try to
free the others. You know the mission. "

LEO PRIME's voice was nothing if not deep and more resonant. "Any
further and we will loose communications. Does anyone have any other
questions before we head in?"

SKY SHADOW had watched silent all this in silence, his optics on
HYDRAS and LEO PRIME. He did said nothing to LEO, instead he whispered
his own orders into his radio, his voice whisper silent, his own
rations carefully stowed away.

(TAG)

Preston
